<class class="guide">
                <h4>How to Use:</h4>
                <ol>
                    <li>Enter keywords or a full title in the input field.</li>
                    <li>Select the type of generation you want (Title or Proposal).</li>
                    <li>Select a field of study from the dropdown menu.</li>
                    <li>Click the "Generate" button to get your title or proposal.</li>
                    <li>You can also delete, copy, or download the generated titles.</li>
                </ol>
                <h4>Note:</h4>
                <p>Make sure to provide relevant keywords for better results.</p>
                <p>Generated titles are suggestions and should be reviewed before use.</p>
                <h4>Disclaimer:</h4>
                <p>This tool is for educational purposes only. The generated titles may not be suitable for all projects.</p>
                <p>Always consult with your advisor or mentor before finalizing your project title.</p>     
